        "text": "=🎬 *YouTube Content Ready for Review*\n\n📌 *Topic:* {{ $json.topic }}\n🆔 *ID:* `{{ $json.content_id }}`\n\n📝 *Title:*\n_{{ $json.youtube_title }}_\n\n🎣 *30-sec Hook:*\n{{ $json.hook_30sec }}\n\n📸 *Thumbnail Concept:*\n{{ $json.thumbnail_concept }}\n\n🇬🇧 *Instagram EN:*\n{{ $json.instagram_caption_en.substring(0, 300) }}...\n\n📱 *TikTok:*\n{{ $json.tiktok_caption }}\n\n🎨 *Pollo AI:* Video generating in background — check taskId in Sheets\n\n——\nApprove to publish to YouTube, Instagram, TikTok, Facebook",
